N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2836.2 - Contractual

State Regulations

The division may contract with municipal and other public
agencies, and with private persons, firms and corporations, for the rendering
of technical services and assistance to qualified applicants. Notes
